data.name: Are you sure you want to delete this role?
data.value: Er du sikker på, at du vil slette denne rolle?

data.name: This action is irreversible. You are about to permanently delete the following role:
data.value: Denne handling kan ikke fortrydes. Du er ved at slette følgende rolle permanent:

data.name: This role is managed by an OpenID Connect (OIDC) provider. Deleting the role here will only remove it from this application. The role will still exist on your OIDC provider and may reappear after the next sync or if the user logs in again. To permanently delete this role, you must remove them from your OIDC provider.
data.value: Denne rolle administreres af en OpenID Connect (OIDC)-udbyder. Hvis du sletter rollen her, fjernes den kun fra denne applikation. Rollen vil stadig eksistere på din OIDC-udbyder og kan komme til syne igen efter næste synkronisering eller hvis brugeren logger ind igen. For at slette denne rolle permanent, skal du fjerne den fra din OIDC-udbyder.
